<p>Hi,</p>

<p>
  The automated BACS check ran on <strong><%= @run_date %></strong> and
  <strong>all <%= @expenses.size %> approved <%= "expense".pluralize(@expenses.size) %> passed</strong>
  — both the automated readiness checks and the AI receipt review.
</p>

<p>The EUSA draft email has been created in the send mailbox. Please review and send it:</p>

<% if @draft_link.present? %>
  <p style="margin: 1.5em 0;">
    <a href="<%= @draft_link %>" style="background-color: #0078d4; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-family: sans-serif;">Open draft in Outlook</a>
  </p>
<% end %>

<p><strong>Batch summary:</strong></p>
<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="4" style="border-collapse: collapse; font-family: sans-serif; margin-bottom: 1em;">
  <thead style="background-color: #f0f0f0;">
    <tr><th>#</th><th>Payee</th><th>Amount</th><th>Budget</th><th>Description</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <% @expenses.each do |expense| %>
      <tr>
        <td>#<%= expense[:auto_number] %></td>
        <td><%= expense[:payee_name] %></td>
        <td>&pound;<%= expense[:amount] %></td>
        <td><%= expense[:budget_name] %></td>
        <td><%= expense[:description] %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
  <tfoot style="background-color: #f0f0f0; font-weight: bold;">
    <tr><td colspan="2">Total</td><td>&pound;<%= @total %></td><td colspan="2"></td></tr>
  </tfoot>
</table>

<p>Producer notification emails have also been sent to payees.</p>

<p>Best,<br>Bedlam Fringe BACS (automated)</p>
